This is awesome!<p>I&#x27;ll certainly contribute to this. Will the source be opened up?<p>Here&#x27;s a delay filter:<p><pre><code>  var delay_array = [];
  var delay_length = 5;
  var delay_feedback = 0.6;
  var delay_volume = 0.4;

  function delay(x) {

    y = 0;

    if (delay_array.length < (delay_length * 1000)) {
      delay_array.push(x);  
    } else {
      y = delay_array.shift();
      delay_array.push(x + (y*delay_feedback));  
    }

    return (x) + ( y * delay_volume );

  }
</code></pre>
Include this in the DSP return code, ie;<p><pre><code>  return delay(synth);</code></pre>
